[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "さて、どうしたものかな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00472",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "個人間のいさかいには、被害が出なければ監察官も\n容易には踏み込めないのだが……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00473",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "……あ、そういえば！　",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00474",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "「九偉人図」について\n調べてみたら、確かに取引の記録がありました！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00475",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "えっ、そ、それはとても助かるっすわ！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00476",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "「九偉人図」は元々ブラオールのとある商会が\n４枚を所持していたようでした",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00477",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "ですが商会の事業拡大や資金繰りのため、\nすべて寄贈されたり売却されたりしていまして……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00478",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "そのうちの１枚がケイウンに贈られていたんです",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00479",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "他の「九偉人図」で、\n行き先が分かっているものは……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00480",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "はい、直近で取引があったのはベスティラ。\n獣人たちの島ですね。そこの王様が持っています",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00481",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "なんでも明るくて荒っぽい島みたいですよ。\n私たちも１週間後に出張で行くんですけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00482",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "商会から許可を得てきた情報はともかく、\n我々の行動まで開示してどうする",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00483",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "はぅあ！　す、すみませんボス……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00484",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "１週間後かぁ……島までご一緒させていただくのって\nありよりのありですかね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00485",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "こちらとしても、監察官が一緒ですと、\n色々と助かりまして",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00486",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "……気になることがある",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00487",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "さっきも今後１週間は平和と言っていたな？\n逆に言えば、１週間後に何か起こるということか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00488",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ええ。でも、それまでには決着を付けておくわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00489",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "は、はぁ……決着、ですか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00490",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "こちらとしては話し合いで解決できるなら\nそれに越したことはないんだけど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00491",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "期限までにできることをしましょう。\nまずはみんなで何ができるのか、相談ね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00492",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "うん、そうだね。\nそれじゃあ……ご迷惑をおかけしました！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00493",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "行っちゃったが……本当に事情聴取しないでいいの？\n思わせぶりなことばっかり言ってたけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_00494",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "ああ。彼女たちは確かに何か匂う……だが、\n決して悪人でもない。そう感じた",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00495",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "常に最前線にいる人間の直感は大事だね。\nともかく……平穏無事を祈るばかりだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_00496",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]